ygData.messageBody:
Try selling your Enchanter research material on the Enchanter board at:

http://www.sitepowerup.com/mb/view.asp?Action=Display&BoardID=102010

msgs scroll off within 5-48 hours depending on posting activity, so you
might want to repost your goods list every so often. It'd also help if you
told your prospective buyers exactly which pages you have.

good luck,

qq
